  "_comment": "Jue Ming Valley / Jueming Valley (\u7edd\u547d\u8c37) \u2014 a valley on Planet Suzaku. Canon (CANON_RI_COMPLETE_WORLD.md L46): the Jue Ming Valley tokens grant access to the Foreign Battleground / Extraterrestrial Battlefield (\u57df\u5916\u6218\u573a), a sealed battlefield outside normal Suzaku geography. The valley is a gateway region \u2014 its geography is defined by the ancient tokens and the sealed rift to the Foreign Battleground. World-law tier: low (Core Formation ceiling) at the surface, but the rift to the Foreign Battleground exposes higher-tier Qi in pockets. Prime Directive: the valley's geography exists independently of the rift; the rift exists independently of the tokens. The tokens are the only safe way through; without one, a cultivator who enters the rift is lost.",
